From 06240af6c9aded4aafdbe39a6ab7f4adfdfb2507 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Faisal Khan <mfkhan@sofi.org>
Date: Sun, 26 Apr 2026 00:21:06 -0700
Subject: [PATCH 03/12] feat(hero): layered boot sequence + pointer parallax +
 token shimmer
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

Adds a curated, theme-aligned motion package to the hero route. Every
new effect is GPU-friendly (transform / opacity / clip-path /
background-position), short-circuited by prefers-reduced-motion via the
global rule plus explicit local overrides, and skipped on coarse
pointers / SSR where it cannot help.

Boot sequence (CSS-only, runs once on initial paint):
- `>_ Hello, I'm` types in via a steps(10) typewriter on width.
- Hero name reveals left → right with a clip-path inset wipe so the
  existing diagonal gradient stays intact (per-letter cascade was
  rejected because inline-block children would re-sample the
  gradient and break the diagonal).
- Title fades up; a terminal caret (▍) blinks after it using the
  shared `cursor-blink` keyframe with a delayed fade-in.
- Summary, .highlight tokens (staggered shimmer), action buttons,
  and social row all enter on a choreographed timeline.

Pointer effects (browser-only, attached in afterNextRender):
- Single rAF-batched pointermove listener writes `--pointer-x` /
  `--pointer-y` (0–1 floats) on the host element, with cleanup via
  DestroyRef.
- Two `.glow-wrapper` parents translate ±28 px in opposite
  directions for a depth parallax; the inner `.glow` keeps its
  existing `pulse` scale animation (no transform conflict).
- A `.hero-spotlight` radial gradient follows the cursor via the
  same vars; opacity gates on `[data-pointer-active='true']` so
  SSR / touch / reduced-motion users never see a pinned center
  glow.

Token + interaction polish:
- `.highlight` spans (Full-Stack Development, Cloud Architecture,
  DevOps) get a syntax-highlighter sweep on first paint, staggered
  150 ms apart via inline `--shimmer-delay`.
- Social links lift with translateY + scale + accent-glow shadow on
  hover / focus, with a tighter 60 ms transition on :active for the
  press rebound.

Verified: ng test hero.component.spec.ts (8/8), npm run typecheck,
npm run build (no new warnings).

Made-with: Cursor
